OL,3,CFuneral held for former Ulster
OL,4,CUnionist MP Martin Smyth
OL,6,FFormer Ulster Unionist MP Rev Martin
OL,7,FSmyth had a career defined by
OL,8,Fintegrity and strong Christian
OL,9,Fprinciple, a church service has heard.
OL,11,FRev Smyth, a Presbyterian minister who
OL,12,Fserved as South Belfast MP for more
OL,13,Fthan 20 years and also led the Orange
OL,14,FOrder during the height of the
OL,15,FTroubles in Northern Ireland, died
OL,16,Flast week at the age of 94.
OL,18,FA service of thanksgiving for his life
OL,19,Fwas held in north Belfast on Friday in
OL,20,FAlexandra Presbyterian Church, where
OL,21,Fhe once was minister.
