OL,3,CFuneral held for former Ulster
OL,4,CUnionist MP Martin Smyth
OL,6,FRev Johnston Lambe, who was Rev
OL,7,FSmyth's own minister for 25 years,
OL,8,Ftold the service how his long-time
OL,9,Ffriend was driven to enter politics
OL,10,Fafter the IRA murder of then-South
OL,11,FBelfast UUP MP Rev Robert Bradford in
OL,12,F1981. He won the subsequent by-
OL,13,Felection the following year.
OL,15,F"He wrestled long over that decision
OL,16,Fand I remember chatting about this,"
OL,17,Fsaid Rev Lambe.
