OL,6,F"Many of his friends tried to persuade
OL,7,Fhim to remain in ministry, some even
OL,8,Fcalled it foolish. However, he
OL,9,Fbelieved that God was calling him to
OL,10,Fthis work but he never resigned as a
OL,11,Fminister of the Presbyterian Church in
OL,12,FIreland, remaining under the care of
OL,13,FNorth Belfast Presbytery."
OL,15,FThe service heard how Rev Smyth
OL,16,Fhimself became a target for the IRA,
OL,17,Fwith a bomb once planted at a church
OL,18,Fmanse where the family lived.
