OL,4,CUnionist MP Martin Smyth
OL,6,F"This left the whole family living
OL,7,Funder great pressure, eventually
OL,8,Fhaving to move house," recalled Rev
OL,9,FLambe.
OL,11,FIn 1995, Rev Smyth ran for the
OL,12,Fleadership of the UUP, but lost out to
OL,13,FDavid Trimble.
OL,15,FCurrent UUP leader Mike Nesbitt was
OL,16,Famong mourners at Friday's service.
OL,17,FDUP leader Gavin Robinson and TUV
OL,18,Fleader Jim Allister also attended.
OL,20,FRev Lambe told mourners that Northern
OL,21,FIreland had "lost a statesman".
