OL,3,CFuneral held for former Ulster
OL,4,CUnionist MP Martin Smyth
OL,6,FThe minister extended sympathies to
OL,7,FRev Smyth's daughters Rosemary and
OL,8,FHeather and the wider family. The
OL,9,Fformer MP was predeceased by his late
OL,10,Fwife Kathleen and late daughter
OL,11,FMargaret.
OL,13,F"His career stands as one of integrity
OL,14,Fand strong Christian principle, never
OL,15,Fafraid to call out wrong doing and
OL,16,Falways ready to show compassion," said
OL,17,FRev Lambe.
